Interpolation

What is Interpolation?
Dynamic data which is stored on app.component.ts file can be displayed on app.component.html page 
with the help of interpolation.


what can we do with Interpolation?
Inside double braces, it works like javascript {{2+2}} ----> It will return the output as 4, eg {{title=="blog"}}
if it satisfies the condition it will return true else false


what we cannot do with Interpolation?
we cannot check type of inside interpolation, increment and decrement operator wont work in interpolation,
initialization wont work , eg {{new title}}

Interview Question

<h1 class="{{title}}"> {{title}} </h1>, we can add classes also in interpolation.